186
00:14:05.750 --> 00:14:07.650
<i>Evet, evet, evet, evet!</i>

187
00:14:07.750 --> 00:14:09.850
Burada sahilde hallediyorlar.

188
00:15:10.050 --> 00:15:13.150
- Selam, Liv.
- Selam, tatlım.


189
00:15:13.450 --> 00:15:15.550
